caption.p: Mortality (%) of Tenebrio molitor ( A) and Harmonia axyridis ( B). The fenvalerate LC 50 values were estimated for the larvae and nymphs of H. longicornis by the packet test. Data are presented as mean ± SE ( n = 5). Different letters indicate significant difference (Kruskal–Wallis/Student-Newman-Keuls, p < 0.01). For abbreviations, see Fig. 1
